{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},"metadata":{"title":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B36ThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProviderC","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Class","symbolKind":"class"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for text area component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the text area component tokens you want.","","        override var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingBlockXl }","        override var sizeMinHeightInput: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._1000 }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: TextAreaComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own space and size semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider(","                                            sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                            spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing"},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.17.0","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Since","type":"aside"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextareacomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent08TextAreaB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\